data.description: Remodeled Pocono vacation home 2 blocks from the beach in popular Towamensing Trails where Short Term Rentals are allowed! Has Central Air!! The spacious living room boasts floor-to-ceiling stone fireplace, cathedral ceilings, new Pergo floors, & bright sliders to expansive deck ! The kitchen features paneled oak cabinets, recessed lighting, breakfast bar, & leads to the elegant dining room with exquisite chandelier & new floors. The large master suite boasts Pergo flooring, dramatic vaulted ceiling with skylight, Jacuzzi tub, full bathroom, & French doors to Juliette balcony! The additional spacious bedrooms have plush carpeting, large closets, & vaulted ceilings. The expansive family room has a huge media/game room & laundry area as well! Don't forget the oversized 1-car garage & shed!
